  <brief_title>Gastric Procedures for Obesity</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of Comparing Outcomes of Laparoscopic Sleeve Gastrectomy, Laparoscopic Roux-en-Y Gastric Bypass and Laparoscopic Gastric Banding to Treat Morbid Obesity</official_title>
